<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="csrf-token" content={get_csrf_token()} />
    <.live_title default="AstraAutoEx">{assigns[:page_title]}</.live_title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href={~p"/favicon.svg"} />
    <link phx-track-static rel="stylesheet" href={~p"/assets/css/app.css"} />
    <script defer phx-track-static type="text/javascript" src={~p"/assets/js/app.js"}>
    </script>
    <script>
      if (localStorage.getItem('theme') === 'dark') document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
    </script>
  </head>

  <body class="glass-page">
    <nav class="glass-nav sticky top-0 z-50 px-6 py-3">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex items-center justify-between">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 no-underline">
            <img src={~p"/images/logo.svg"} alt="AstraAuto" class="h-7" />
          </a>
          <button
            onclick="document.getElementById('changelog-modal').style.display='flex'"
            class="hidden sm:inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)] border border-[var(--glass-stroke-base)] rounded-full px-3 py-1 hover:border-[var(--glass-accent-from)] hover:text-[var(--glass-text-primary)] transition-all cursor-pointer"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-3.5 h-3.5"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z" /><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5" /><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5" />
            </svg>
            Beta v0.9.8
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 pr-2">
          <%= if @current_scope do %>
            <a
              href={~p"/home"}
              class="nav-link flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-[var(--glass-text-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--glass-text-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--glass-bg-muted)] transition-all"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-4 h-4"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" /><path d="M8 21h8" /><path d="M12 17v4" />
              </svg>
              {dgettext("default", "Workspace")}
            </a>
            <a
              href={~p"/asset-hub"}
              class="nav-link flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-[var(--glass-text-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--glass-text-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--glass-bg-muted)] transition-all"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-4 h-4"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path d="M22 19a2 2 0 01-2 2H4a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5l2 3h9a2 2 0 012 2z" />
                <path d="M12 11v6" /><path d="M9 14h6" />
              </svg>
              {dgettext("default", "Asset Hub")}
            </a>
            <a
              href={~p"/guide"}
              class="nav-link flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-[var(--glass-text-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--glass-text-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--glass-bg-muted)] transition-all"
              title={dgettext("default", "User Guide")}
            >
              <svg
                class="w-4 h-4"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 014 4v14a3 3 0 00-3-3H2z" /><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 00-4 4v14a3 3 0 013-3h7z" />
              </svg>
              {dgettext("default", "Guide")}
            </a>
            <a
              href={~p"/short-drama"}
              class="nav-link flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-[var(--glass-text-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--glass-text-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--glass-bg-muted)] transition-all"
              title="短剧工作台"
            >
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.59 14.37a6 6 0 01-5.84 7.38v-4.8m5.84-2.58a14.98 14.98 0 006.16-12.12A14.98 14.98 0 009.631 8.41m5.96 5.96a14.926 14.926 0 01-5.841 2.58m-.119-8.54a6 6 0 00-7.381 5.84h4.8m2.581-5.84a14.927 14.927 0 00-2.58 5.84m2.699 2.7c-.103.021-.207.041-.311.06a15.09 15.09 0 01-2.448-2.448 14.9 14.9 0 01.06-.312m-2.24 2.39a4.493 4.493 0 00-1.757 4.306 4.493 4.493 0 004.306-1.758M16.5 9a1.5 1.5 0 11-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 013 0z" />
              </svg>
              短剧
            </a>
            <a
              href={~p"/assistant"}
              class="nav-link flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-[var(--glass-text-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--glass-text-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--glass-bg-muted)] transition-all"
              title="AI 助手"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-4 h-4"
                fill="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09z" />
              </svg>
              AI 助手
            </a>
            <a
              href={~p"/profile"}
              class="nav-link flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-[var(--glass-text-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--glass-text-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--glass-bg-muted)] transition-all"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-4 h-4"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4" /><path d="M20 21a8 8 0 00-16 0" />
              </svg>
              {dgettext("default", "Settings")}
            </a>
            <span class="mx-1.5 h-4 w-px bg-[var(--glass-stroke-base)]"></span>
            <span class="text-xs text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)] hidden lg:inline">
              {@current_scope.user.email}
            </span>
            <.link
              href={~p"/users/log-out"}
              method="delete"
              class="flex items-center gap-1 px-2 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)] hover:text-[var(--glass-text-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--glass-bg-muted)] transition-all"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-4 h-4"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path d="M9 21H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h4" /><polyline points="16 17 21 12 16 7" /><line
                  x1="21"
                  y1="12"
                  x2="9"
                  y2="12"
                />
              </svg>
            </.link>
          <% else %>
            <a
              href={~p"/users/log-in"}
              class="text-sm text-[var(--glass-text-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--glass-text-primary)] transition-colors px-3 py-1.5"
            >
              {dgettext("auth", "Sign In")}
            </a>
            <a
              href={~p"/users/register"}
              class="glass-btn glass-btn-primary text-sm py-1.5 px-4"
            >
              {dgettext("auth", "Sign Up")}
            </a>
          <% end %>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)] ml-1">
            <%!-- Theme toggle --%>
            <button
              onclick="document.documentElement.classList.toggle('dark'); localStorage.setItem('theme', document.documentElement.classList.contains('dark') ? 'dark' : 'light')"
              class="p-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-[var(--glass-bg-muted)] transition-colors"
              title="切换主题"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-3.5 h-3.5 dark:hidden"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path d="M21.752 15.002A9.718 9.718 0 0118 15.75c-5.385 0-9.75-4.365-9.75-9.75 0-1.33.266-2.597.748-3.752A9.753 9.753 0 003 11.25C3 16.635 7.365 21 12.75 21a9.753 9.753 0 009.002-5.998z" />
              </svg>
              <svg
                class="w-3.5 h-3.5 hidden dark:block"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path d="M12 3v2.25m6.364.386l-1.591 1.591M21 12h-2.25m-.386 6.364l-1.591-1.591M12 18.75V21m-4.773-4.227l-1.591 1.591M5.25 12H3m4.227-4.773L5.636 5.636M15.75 12a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0z" />
              </svg>
            </button>
            <span class="opacity-20 text-xs">|</span>
            <a
              href="?locale=en"
              class="hover:text-[var(--glass-text-primary)] transition-colors text-xs px-1"
            >
              EN
            </a>
            <span class="opacity-30 text-xs">|</span>
            <a
              href="?locale=zh"
              class="hover:text-[var(--glass-text-primary)] transition-colors text-xs px-1"
            >
              中文
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <%!-- Changelog Modal --%>
    <div
      id="changelog-modal"
      style="display:none"
      class="fixed inset-0 z-[100] flex items-center justify-center"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-sm"
        onclick="document.getElementById('changelog-modal').style.display='none'"
      >
      </div>

      <div
        class="relative bg-[var(--glass-bg-surface)] border border-[var(--glass-stroke-base)] rounded-2xl shadow-2xl max-w-lg w-full mx-4 max-h-[80vh] overflow-hidden flex flex-col"
        style="backdrop-filter: blur(20px)"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 border-b border-[var(--glass-stroke-soft)]">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--glass-text-primary)]">更新日志</h3>

            <p class="text-xs text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)]">AstrAuto Drama 版本历史</p>
          </div>

          <button
            onclick="document.getElementById('changelog-modal').style.display='none'"
            class="text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)] hover:text-[var(--glass-text-primary)] text-xl"
          >
            &times;
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto px-6 py-4 space-y-6 text-sm">
          <%!-- v0.9.8 --%>
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold bg-green-500/20 text-green-400">
                最新
              </span>
              <span class="font-bold text-[var(--glass-text-primary)]">v0.9.8</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)]">2026-04-16</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)] mb-1.5 italic">
              apiyi VEO 3.1 横屏首尾帧打通 + 4 个 async 链路 P0 修复
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-[var(--glass-text-secondary)] list-disc list-inside text-xs">
              <li><strong>🎬 apiyi VEO 3.1 landscape-fast-fl 真跑通</strong>：Panel 06347c45 生成 r2cdn.copilotbase.com 视频，完整异步链路打通</li>
              <li><strong>P0 修复模型名双重 transform</strong>：handler 里 apply_model_suffix 产生 "veo-3.1-fast-landscape-fl" 错序，改为完全交给 apiyi provider 内部转换</li>
              <li><strong>P0 修复 Req multipart 格式</strong>：build_file_part 从 3-tuple 改为 2-tuple &quot;name + data + opts&quot;，才被 Req 接受</li>
              <li><strong>P0 修复 AsyncPoller config 查找</strong>：external_id 前缀 "OPENAI" 要先映射到 "apiyi" 再 Map.get，之前 config 永远是 %{}</li>
              <li><strong>P0 修复 external_id 解析</strong>：apiyi 用 "OPENAI:VIDEO:token:video_id" 4 段格式，解析时剥离 base64 token 拿真正的 video_id</li>
              <li><strong>修 header content-type list 格式</strong>：新版 Req 返回 list 而非 string，pattern match 加 list 分支</li>
              <li><strong>VideoPanel auto-FL 模式</strong>：新增 find_next_panel_image/1，自动用下一 panel image 作为 last_frame</li>
              <li><strong>🎞️ 4.5MB 混合视频合成</strong>：2 真 AI 视频（1 MiniMax + 1 apiyi VEO）+ 11 静态图 + 字幕 + TTS，比 v0.9.7 多 1.1MB</li>
              <li><strong>观察</strong>：VEO 3.1 对"少女"类场景触发内容审核误判（3/3 批量失败），需 prompt/image 规避或等模型更新</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <%!-- v0.9.7 --%>
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">
                历史
              </span>
              <span class="font-bold text-[var(--glass-text-primary)]">v0.9.7</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)]">2026-04-16</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)] mb-1.5 italic">
              混合 AI 视频合成 + 短剧 3 步串联 + 分享页上线
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-[var(--glass-text-secondary)] list-disc list-inside text-xs">
              <li><strong>🎬 混合 AI 视频合成</strong>：1 真 MiniMax 视频 + 12 静态图 + 字幕 + 中文旁白 → 3.4MB / 52s 完整短剧</li>
              <li><strong>🎭 短剧 3 步链验证</strong>：sd_topic_selection → sd_story_outline → sd_character_dev 连续完成，上下文通过 load_previous_result 串联</li>
              <li><strong>🔗 视频分享页上线</strong>：/m/:public_id 路由渲染 HTML5 video + 标题，首个 episode 分享 URL 已发布</li>
              <li><strong>批量触发 11 个 video_panel 任务</strong>：并发提交，2 成功 9 失败（MiniMax 额度/RPM）</li>
              <li><strong>模型配置修正</strong>：user_preferences 默认 video 模型 minimax-hailuo-2.3 → MiniMax-Hailuo-2.3（API 接受大写）</li>
              <li><strong>VideoCompose 图像 fallback 自动混合</strong>：有 video_url 的用真视频，没有的图像转片段，混合 concat</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <%!-- v0.9.6 --%>
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">
                历史
              </span>
              <span class="font-bold text-[var(--glass-text-primary)]">v0.9.6</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)]">2026-04-16</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)] mb-1.5 italic">
              真实 MiniMax I2V 视频 + 短剧串联 + 4 个 P0 修复
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-[var(--glass-text-secondary)] list-disc list-inside text-xs">
              <li><strong>🎬 真实视频生成跑通</strong>：MiniMax-Hailuo-2.3 异步 I2V，panel 获得真 MP4 URL（OSS CDN）</li>
              <li><strong>P0: TaskRunner 增加 :async 返回语义</strong>：handler 返回 async tuple 时保留 processing 状态，让 AsyncPollWorker 接管轮询</li>
              <li><strong>P0: atomize_keys/1 对非 map 崩</strong>：AsyncPollWorker build_user_config 在 config value 不是 map 时 FunctionClauseError → 加 fallback</li>
              <li><strong>P0: apply_model_suffix 只对 API易</strong>：之前给 MiniMax 加 -landscape/-fl 后缀导致 "invalid params, incorrect model param input"</li>
              <li><strong>P0: first_frame_image 字段映射</strong>：VideoPanel 传 :image_url 但 MiniMax 读 :first_frame_image → handler 同时设置两个字段</li>
              <li><strong>短剧 build_bindings 补 topic_keyword</strong>：之前 sd_topic_selection 没读 topic_keyword，LLM 只能用默认 prompt</li>
              <li><strong>短剧步骤自动串联</strong>：新增 load_previous_result/2 — story_outline 自动读 topic_selection 的 raw 输出作上下文</li>
              <li><strong>MiniMax 视频模型探测</strong>：已验证可用 T2V 模型是 MiniMax-Hailuo-2.3；I2V-01/Director/live 需 first_frame_image</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <%!-- v0.9.5 --%>
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">
                历史
              </span>
              <span class="font-bold text-[var(--glass-text-primary)]">v0.9.5</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)]">2026-04-16</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)] mb-1.5 italic">
              真实 TTS + 有声视频合成 + 短剧 LLM 跑通 + 依赖锁定
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-[var(--glass-text-secondary)] list-disc list-inside text-xs">
              <li><strong>🎙️ 真实 TTS 跑通</strong>：5 条中文旁白 → 32kHz mono WAV 文件，每条 4.47s / 166-281KB</li>
              <li><strong>P0 修复 MiniMax TTS 路径</strong>：get_in 用 Access.get 崩溃 → 改用 pattern match + save_hex_as_wav 保存到 /uploads/voice/</li>
              <li><strong>🎬 有声视频合成</strong>：项目 13 产出 **2.6MB / 48.2s / H.264 视频流 + AAC 44.1kHz stereo 音频流**（比纯图片版大 0.4MB）</li>
              <li><strong>VideoCompose 新增 build_voice_segments/1</strong>：自动从 voice_lines 聚合 audio_path + start_time，传 FFmpeg filter_complex</li>
              <li><strong>resolve_local_audio/2</strong>：把 `/uploads/voice/xxx.wav` 映射到本地文件系统路径供 FFmpeg 消费</li>
              <li><strong>🎭 短剧 sd_topic_selection 真跑成功</strong>：MiniMax LLM 返回 title_candidates + genre + target_audience + tone + episode_count 完整 JSON</li>
              <li><strong>短剧卡片 UI 增强</strong>：依赖锁定（1→2→3→4→5，5→6/7/8），锁定卡片 🔒 标签 + opacity-60 + 按钮 disabled</li>
              <li><strong>短剧结果展示</strong>：task.result 完成后显示"查看结果 ▼"按钮，展开显示 LLM raw text（font-mono + max-h-60 滚动）</li>
              <li><strong>toggle_result / expanded MapSet</strong>：用户可以折叠/展开每步结果独立控制</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <%!-- v0.9.4 --%>
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">
                历史
              </span>
              <span class="font-bold text-[var(--glass-text-primary)]">v0.9.4</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)]">2026-04-16</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-[var(--glass-text-tertiary)] mb-1.5 italic">
              字幕 burn-in + 短剧 8 任务 UI + Panel 编辑器验证 + LipSync schema 修复
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-[var(--glass-text-secondary)] list-disc list-inside text-xs">
              <li><strong>🎉 字幕烧录成功</strong>：帧截图验证白字黑描边中文字幕"[旁白] 雨夜，一个疲惫的身影出现在车库入口"烧到画面底部</li>
              <li><strong>simple_concat 支持字幕</strong>：有 subtitle_path 时走 reencode_concat + subtitles filter 路径</li>
              <li><strong>subtitles filter Windows 路径</strong>：反斜杠→正斜杠 + 冒号转义，force_style ASS 样式</li>
              <li><strong>短剧 8 任务 UI 入口</strong>：新路由 /short-drama + 2x4 卡片网格（选题/大纲/角色/目录/剧本/质检/合规/出海）+ nav 链接</li>
              <li><strong>短剧卡片状态</strong>：每步绑定最新 task 实例，显示 已完成/运行中/失败/排队中 chip + 进度%</li>
              <li><strong>LipSync schema 预防性修复</strong>：Panel 无 :audio_url → 新增 Production.voice_line_for_panel/1 从 VoiceLine 表读 audio</li>
              <li><strong>Panel 编辑器验证</strong>：DB round-trip 测试 7 字段（description/shot_type/camera_move/location/characters/photography_rules/acting_notes）全部正确写入</li>
              <li><strong>审计</strong>：项目 13 首次跑出带字幕的 48 秒 2.2MB mp4，1280x720 H.264</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <%!-- v0.9.3 --%>
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">
                历史
              </span>
